Ballot data

Source: R/fokus.gen.R
ballots.Rd

A list of tibbles containing official statistical data about all FOKUS-covered ballots. The data includes i.a. the total electorate as well as participation numbers per voting channel and per voting decision.

Usage

ballots

Format

A tibble.

See also

Other datasets: elections, proposals, qstnrs

Examples

fokus::ballots
